{"tid":766171,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想養兔仔，邊度買好？","createTime":"2018-08-03T11:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T03:49:00.000Z","uid":197974,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"92d23ff29a69a2e5cb2e8a5fc705b5d67a0c0d65","tid":766171,"uid":197974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:31:38.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"185cefa67a8e07f4f52dd8c8bd536c348e7244eb","tid":766171,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:37:30.000Z","msg":"愛爾蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7857806ea9315eafddbb49cde6b8bb49e04e1d9","tid":766171,"uid":31186,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:51:26.000Z","msg":"兔協領養"},{"pid":"8795b9bc985da5a2f7009c1df397805893e9ad73","tid":766171,"uid":197098,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會領養，這裏有太多兔子正在等新主人帶牠們去新的家，過新的生活。詳情可去<a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114%20&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=7f688861\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114 </a><br />\n<br />\n兔子親吻主人，這是代表你是一個好主人，以下2個videos 可看到： <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMaovq8Vz1LM&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=5dcb9a24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Maovq8Vz1LM</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpyL0yEs-ka8&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=02476fa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8</a> <br />\n兔子高難度技能 - 打鼓、打籃球、簽名: 🐰🐰😊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dLCEU3baplk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdLCEU3baplk&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=76d65a2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dLCEU3baplk</a> </span>"},{"pid":"e02074c8406023669ed99fcaa53b42a8697af249","tid":766171,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:20:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>兔仔開心到極!!【身體語言】+室內養會長壽!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔子跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。當牠們binky 時，這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。兔子也會舒適地躺在地上，伸展手腳，還會打翻騰。兔子在室內飼養會比室外養長命，因為沒有任何天氣和敵人威脅，感到平靜和舒適。以下2個videos 可以看到兔子最開心的時候：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE90ikFGQTqs&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6ce0ae42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FDMWC5U0gkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFDMWC5U0gkw&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=af575d82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FDMWC5U0gkw</a> <br />\n<br />\n兔仔會玩街機遊戲機!! 好利害呀:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XxdMkegP5CA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXxdMkegP5CA&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=10fd969b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XxdMkegP5CA</a> <br />\n<br />\n兔仔畫畫 !!:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-8wPlKkuBB0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-8wPlKkuBB0&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e4a9c993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-8wPlKkuBB0</a> <br />\n<br />\n兔子打籃球:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1yM0rhQxMYI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1yM0rhQxMYI&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=59556b8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1yM0rhQxMYI</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>兔子深入資訊</strong>：<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=2101de2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a> </span>"},{"pid":"bb44adb791f6af6295bbf394bf987bb24a44a6ae","tid":766171,"uid":16031,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:22:57.000Z","msg":"唔好買<br />\n去領養啦<br />\n但要有心理準備<br />\n養兔兔係幾麻煩"},{"pid":"f53f7280ea1f5e715a4bf34f7c2d5c2489ab402a","tid":766171,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:32:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">訓練兔仔🐰去廁所是很簡單的。糞便是沒有臭味的，而且是乾的，所以通常可以拿上來放回和兔子的廁所（牠們便會知道要去廁所大小便）然後洗手。尿有時會有少少味，最好把白醋加水放入噴霧樽，然後清洗地板，這樣的話會立刻清除味道及減少牠們在這裏小便。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下3個videos 有教, 步驟簡單:</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zsB7SILsOns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzsB7SILsOns&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=b6b18f6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zsB7SILsOns</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gP4IaOQsKl4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgP4IaOQsKl4&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8d8f1bb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gP4IaOQsKl4</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GHRkf5z6EQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0GHRkf5z6EQ&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c98ddf60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GHRkf5z6EQ</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>領養兔仔：</strong><a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6e99a2df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a> <br />\n兔子深入資訊：<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=2101de2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a> </span>"},{"pid":"ecafab38202b1c9f90c8f840b95a1642d05760f6","tid":766171,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:37:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">在大自然內，兔仔有牠們的等級制度。一個高級(dominant)的兔仔會groom (舔和梳理) 一個次級(inferior)的兔仔。但高級的亦會要求次級的兔仔groom 牠，這是一定要服從的。當兔仔低頭向前躺在地上，牠就是想你groom (撫摸和親吻) 牠，這樣可以增加牠的自尊心、令牠舒適、快樂、心理健康。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom牠們，令牠們冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。<br />\n<br />\n兔仔是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animal)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。<ins>有時我們看電視的時候，兔子會躺在電視機前面，幸好牠們不知道我們其實不在看牠們。</ins> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下video是一個等級制度的例子, 可以在<ins>0:59</ins> 看到：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNyv4VhuZv_s&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c8dfead3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">關於兔子身體語言：<a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f9526094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a> <br />\n<strong><ins>領養兔仔：</ins></strong><a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6e99a2df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a><br />\n兔子深入資訊：<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=2101de2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a></span>"},{"pid":"bea012252772be0fea6385518b58a77b5aeeb869","tid":766171,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:06:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">為什麼兔仔咬籠子？🐰🐰😊</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n兔子咬籠其實是想引主人注意，覺得悶，告訴主人牠想出來玩和探索。兔子咬東西是自然的，牠們在大自然是用腳和牙齒來掘洞穴。由於牠們的牙齒不斷生長，咬東西可以幫牠們磨短。<strong><ins>喜歡咬東西的兔子是聰明、親切、喜歡引人(或其他兔)注意。</ins></strong>有時候主人正在整理東西，牠們過來其實想一起參與。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_GZZCdCLIKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_GZZCdCLIKo&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=fa1e4c64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_GZZCdCLIKo</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>領養兔仔：</ins></strong><a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6e99a2df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a> <br />\n兔子深入資訊：<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=2101de2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"584ba99648af2744e7a389048a24363c1a1d4595","tid":766171,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:50:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">給兔子無限Hay，可以把不同hay 混合一起，給牠們一些變化，例如：2/3Timothy Hay 和1/3 Oat Hay 或 Orchard grass或brome Hay。會更加好吃😊</span>"},{"pid":"6904a1ba5f5c4d2751b8297518a22c17e2609e02","tid":766171,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:44:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>狗狗搶野食! 兔兔毫無還手之力! 🙈🙈</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔仔是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animal)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。當牠們側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。(你可想像正前方是盲點，側面才看得最清楚，前腳移動有限，又怎會攻擊到他人？）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下video 可看到狗狗搶吃兔糧, 兔兔毫無還手之力😭😆🙈:</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JKwW65LcLIg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJKwW65LcLIg&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=774125ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JKwW65LcLIg</a><br />\nhahaha"},{"pid":"761e91e648f3d977f4150e97b5f75500865fc9c6","tid":766171,"uid":62020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:46:16.000Z","msg":"去兔協"},{"pid":"af4a4292e7c6cd20c56fc98a7c036c1f38a5e201","tid":766171,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兔仔根本係害蟲"},{"pid":"93e9ecad01f45d7759c8f3334ef3b726b9421f2f","tid":766171,"uid":165945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T13:07:59.000Z","msg":"唔好買兔仔，去兔協領養啦<br />\n<br />\n照顧兔仔要好多心機同精神架，佢地要不停食不停痾，每日要清籠換墊材，一養左就日日都要做佢清潔姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fa56b49dfe478cf2b4bb0477f6217417921025","tid":766171,"uid":116143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T13:17:10.000Z","msg":"養大d跟住紅燒兔肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1413beba68de6831aff5a5f5a04d7a3e940f34","tid":766171,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:18:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">怎樣叫兔仔回到籠裡？不要抱!</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal), 在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animals)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚。因此，兔子不喜歡被抱來抱去。當牠逃跑的時候，你還去追住抱，會令兔子和主人的信任更差。最好的方法去叫牠入籠是每晚(比如：22:00）搖零食樽或pellet 樽幾下，再引牠進入籠吃。幾天後，兔子就會記得零食樽的聲音知道是時候回到籠吃。習慣後，牠會自動22:00左右提主人你是時候回到籠裡吃東西。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下video 有教：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RJcvi7o4YXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRJcvi7o4YXA&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=624a1a5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RJcvi7o4YXA</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>領養兔仔:</ins></strong> <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6e99a2df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a><br />\n兔子深入資訊：<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=2101de2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a><br />\n更多關於兔子的身體語言(開心、憂愁、憤怒、驚慌)： <a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f9526094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a> </span>"},{"pid":"85e20bcd6be6d7356654ffd18b084bee5340f11b","tid":766171,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:39:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果你在兔兔面前打開手掌，對於牠來說是要求牠groom 你。如果主人和兔兔的關係好，牠會groom主人。如果牠對主人感到憤怒，對於牠來說，在牠面前打開手掌是不尊重牠，牠可能會用屁股對着你(代表生悶氣) 或嚴重的話，撲過來咬你。兔子憤怒的時候，耳朵會放在後面，耳口向側，姿勢站起來很硬對着你。(這個耳朵擺放姿勢同驚慌一樣，但驚慌時坐姿會蹲下。大家可以看我寫兔子驚慌的post) 以下video 是主人要求兔兔groom 主人的例子：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6DKeKyzZ67Y&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8a3d5afe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><ins>有趣視頻:</ins></em></strong></span> 兩隻兔子正在決定等級制度，但遇到困難。兔子A groom 兔子B, 但groom 了很久和等了很久還未得到回報(兔子B groom A作為回報)，所以發脾氣在2:08咬兔子B。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Faf7_mGuD5Qg&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e1976060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg</a></span>"},{"pid":"1065e524fd1e4e0f3d23d0813036eda7b6a57a30","tid":766171,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:49:00.000Z","msg":"🐰領養了兔兔，改變了牠的生命！牠還會經常binky(跳兔子舞) ! 🤩<br />\n<br />\n(兔子binky是兔子最開心的狀態。當牠們binky 時，這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMu27kYckovg&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=60a7629b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg</a><br />\n<br />\n實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會領養，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6e99a2df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"}]}